LG Electronics Says It Aims to Be No. 1 in 3-D TV

-- B y   J u n   Y a n g
-- 
2011-02-16T07:10:22Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-16/lg-electronics-says-it-aims-to-be-no-1-in-3-d-tv-correct-.html
  LG Electronics Inc . aims to become
the biggest in the world in 3-D televisions, Choi Sang Gyu, the
company’s head of marketing for the Korean market, said in  Seoul 
today.  He didn’t elaborate on a timeframe.  To contact the reporter on this story:
